&#10;&#10;Passing an empty domain will delete all metadata. Passing an empty key will&#10;delete all metadata for the given domain.&#10;&#10;@param string $domain The domain name&#10;@param string $key    The key" ilk="function" line="53" lineend="53" name="deleteMetadata" signature="deleteMetadata(string $key = '', string $domain = 'messages')"><variable citdl="string" default="''" ilk="argument" line="53" name="key" /><variable citdl="string" default="'messages'" ilk="argument" line="53" name="domain" /></scope></scope></scope></scope>